thread.title: Robbie Ibrahim
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Robbie Ibrahim

author: Robbie Ibrahim
title: Robbie Ibrahim
text: Anthony Gentile has managed my properties for a number of years and I cannot recommend him highly enough. His knowledge of the rental market, advice and all round communication sets the standard in real estate management. I have and never will look elsewhere as the service levels are consistently high and more often than not exceed expectations.
